{"ID":"20260609133144-5fk2xsj","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609133144-5fk2xsj","title":"2020年全国Ⅲ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609133144-jdoqxg3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133144-jdoqxg3","updated":"20260609133157"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文化是一个民族的灵魂。五千年的中华文化体现的中华民族的精神追求，已成为中华民族区别于其他民族的精神标识。而其基本价值已积淀为中华民族的文化基因，成为中华民族的精神命脉。（         ）。中华文化与中华民族"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":" "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，中国人之所以为中国人的特性，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"不是生理的，而且是文化的、精神的因素"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"；没有中华文化，中国人就不成其为中国人，中华民族就不成其为中华民族。中华文化的精神品格与价值追求，支撑了几千年来中华民族的繁衍生息和"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，今天仍然是而且未来必将还是我们发展壮大的强大精神力量。中华文化的精神特质就是我们今天要大力弘扬的“中国精神”，而弘扬中国精神，是凝聚中国力量、走稳中国道路的关键。没有中华文化的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":" "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，就没有中华民族的伟大复兴。放到世界文明史中看，中华民族创造的的中华文化具有独特的文化传统，独特的价值体系，独特的民族色彩，独特的历史进程，其长期的演化过程造就了我们的文化认同，赋予我们生命力和创造力，也决定了我们独特的发展路径。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133144-rgrnln3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133144-rgrnln3","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-bs68bbd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-bs68bbd","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．下列在文中括号内补写的语句，最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-wfdlre7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-wfdlre7","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．传承中华文化就是维系中华民族的精神命脉"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-seem8og","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-seem8og","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．传承中华文化必须维系中华民族的精神命脉"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-l6juj8y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-l6juj8y","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．维系中华民族的精神命脉就是传承中华文化"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-71u3lkr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-71u3lkr","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．维系中华民族的精神命脉就能传承中华文化"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-a8dje76","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-a8dje76","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．依次填入文中横线上的词语，全都恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-99j796s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-99j796s","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．一脉相承    薪火相传    博大精深    源远流长"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-e1dchb6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-e1dchb6","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．互为一体    前赴后继    博大精深    卓尔不群"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-94avrg8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-94avrg8","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．互为一体    薪火相传    繁荣昌盛    源远流长"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-cqoybzj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-cqoybzj","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．一脉相承    前赴后继    繁荣昌盛    卓尔不群"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-6opluye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-6opluye","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．文中画横线的部分有语病，下列修改最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-8ydblt6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-8ydblt6","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．不是生理的因素，而是文化的、精神的"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-b9ajubw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-b9ajubw","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．不是生理的，而是文化的、精神的"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-ea15z9l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-ea15z9l","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．不仅是生理的，而是文化的、精神的"}]},{"ID":"20260609133208-8dv6knm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133208-8dv6knm","updated":"20260609133208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．不仅是生理的因素，而是文化的、精神的"}]},{"ID":"20260609133144-6vdo69t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133144-6vdo69t","updated":"20260609133215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609133144-wl5pde3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133144-wl5pde3","updated":"20260609133215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．A    18．C    19．B"}]},{"ID":"20260609133144-4bafbwx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133144-4bafbwx","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-my5dtqs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-my5dtqs","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．本题考查简明、连贯、得体的能力。填写衔接句主要从陈述对象的一致、虚词的运用、句式选用、情感基调、前后的逻辑顺序和音韵和谐的角度选择。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-4jyt070","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-4jyt070","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文段论述中华文化和中华民族的关系，根据后文“中华文化与中华民族”可知，文化在前，民族在后，据此排除CD；再根据后文“中华文化与中华民族互为一体”，说明二者是对等关系，即“传承中华文化就是维系中华民族的精神命脉”，排除B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-nr2z7ge","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-nr2z7ge","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-hllu41x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-hllu41x","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．此题考查考生正确辨析和使用成语的能力。此类题一般从三个方面综合考虑分析即成语的基本义、感情色彩和语境。需要注意色彩不明，断词取义，对象误用，谦敬错位，功能混乱，不合语境，望文生义等错误使用类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-3mdxfez","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-3mdxfez","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一脉相承：意思是从同一血统、派别世代相承流传下来。比喻某种思想、行为或学说之间有继承关系。互为一体：互相融合，成为一体。语境强调二者的相互交融，本是一个整体，因此选“互为一体。”排除AD。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-atgs4fk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-atgs4fk","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"薪火相传：比喻学问和技艺代代相传。前赴后继：形容奋勇前进，连续不断。此处强调中华文化代代相传，故选“薪火相传”。排除B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-w3w13zo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-w3w13zo","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"博大精深：形容思想和学术广博高深。多用于形容理论、学识、思想、作品等广博丰富，深奥精微。繁荣昌盛：指国家兴旺发达，欣欣向荣。此处强调中华文化的兴旺发达，从而使中华民族得以伟大复兴，故选“繁荣昌盛”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-d6dtipm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-d6dtipm","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"源远流长：比喻历史悠久，根底深厚。卓尔不群：指才德超出寻常，与众不同。语境是中华文化，不是人，选“源远流长”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-fp1dweo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-fp1dweo","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-l1finwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-l1finwn","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．此题考核辨析并修改病句的能力。注意明确病句的类型,以及典型的错例，答题时从结构和内容的角度分析句子，对照错例，找到错误。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-mqzirfj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-mqzirfj","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"原句关联词搭配不当，应为“不是……而是”，“不仅……而且”，据此排除CD；文段强调中华文化是中国人的精神命脉，因此，应为“不是生理的，而是文化的、精神的”，A项“因素”赘余，排除A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133227-3tkhg11","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133227-3tkhg11","updated":"20260609133227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]}]}